    &quot;surface&quot;: {
      &quot;$type&quot;: &quot;color&quot;,
      &quot;$value&quot;: {
        &quot;light&quot;: &quot;#ffffff&quot;,
        &quot;dark&quot;: &quot;#000000&quot;
      }
    }
  }
}

The $extensions.modes documents expected modes but does not enforce them. Validation should check mode consistency.
